   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Herakleides to Ptolemaios, farmer of Tebtunis, greeting. Do not give anything as security to Komon son of Komon, for nothing whatsoever! Goodbye. The 22nd year, Epeiph 17.</ab>
